nodes.text: The Humbar were an influential political dynasty within the Galactic Republic. In 104 ABY, Doctor Gabrel Treon mentioned the Humbar in Tinker, Tailor, Soldier, Praji: A Cartel of Genes, a history of the Praji family that was published in the Byblos Journal of Historical Science.
Nathan O'Keefe, the author of Tinker, Tailor, Soldier, Praji, mentioned the Humbar as a reference to the planet Humbarine, and he speculated that the Humbar were the world's original colonists.
